Common.Highlight.Common.Text: 10 car parks with 2 under cover parks
Would suit a variety of businesses

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer this well presented two storey office to the market. The property offers approximately 328 square metres of high quality office accommodation and storage.

The ground level consists of a reception area, kitchen, boardroom and storage (with roller door access).

Level 1 provides 2 offices, store room and a large open plan area, perfect for work-stations or additional offices.


Other features include:

- Great natural light throughout, data cabling, goods lift, reverse cycle air-conditioning and security system.

- 10 car parks are associated with the property with 2 being under cover. The property is well secured with fencing. Additional parking is prevalent at the front of the property and directly opposite in the Adelaide Showgrounds car-park. The Adelaide Showground Railway Station is located some 100 metres to the west of the property.

- Neat, tidy and versatile office that would meet the needs of any business seeking a corporate office.

Lease Term: Negotiable
Options: Negotiable

Date Available: Immediately

18 on-site car parks that are included in the rental plus excellent signage opportunities compliment this offering.
